OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe final visit is to Moran's B&B
OL,7,     Fin Westward Ho! in Devon, owned by
OL,8,     Fultra-chic retirees John and
OL,9,     FJaqueline. But Christine and Ian
OL,10,     Faren't impressed by the lack of an
OL,11,     Fensuite.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,14,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,15,     Ffor the last time. After dramatic
OL,16,     Fdiscoveries and cutting comments,
OL,17,     Fthe payments are revealed and the
OL,18,     Fwinner is announced.
