OL,5,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,6,     FGeorge visits a handsome,
OL,7,     Fturn-of-the-century terrace home,
OL,8,     Fwhose new owners are set on a
OL,9,     Fmonochrome colour scheme, and a
OL,10,     Fworkshop that makes antique-effect
OL,11,     Fmirrors.
OL,12,G1855 Location, Location, Location
